---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Dermatology — Entry Requirements" description="ACD dermatology training entry requirements and selection process.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Entry Requirements</h1>
    <p>Dermatology — ACD</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Registered medical practitioner with resident status in Australia</li>
      <li>Completion of the specified medical training program outlined in the ACD Training Program Handbook and Curriculum</li>
      <li>Entry is highly competitive — limited positions available nationally</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Selection Process</h2>
    <p>Applicants are assessed across <strong>5 areas</strong> that contribute to an overall rating determining progression to the next round.</p>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Academic record and CV</li>
      <li>Clinical and non-clinical work experience</li>
      <li>Commitment to rural and regional dermatology workforce</li>
      <li>Research and publications</li>
      <li>Interview — Multiple Mini-Interviews (MMIs) aligned with the Dermatological Competencies</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Multiple Mini-Interviews (MMIs)</div>
      <p>Shortlisted applicants demonstrate real-life knowledge and experience from clinical and non-clinical settings through a series of structured MMI stations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
